description: THE INFAMOUS 'California Burrito'--Stuffed with Carne Asada(marinated steak), shredded cheese, Seasoned TATER TOTS(Yep-they're INSIDE the burrito!),Fresh Truck-Made MILD SALSA, and smooth sour cream. VEGGIE BURRITO--Our own Southwest Quinoa("keen-wah"), Seasoned Tater Tots, Shredded Cheese, Fresh Truck-Made MILD SALSA, and smooth sour cream.Rotating menu of delicious SOFT GRILLED FLATBREAD SANDWICHES** including:The Outlaw--Steak, Bacon, Monterey Jack Cheese Sauce, Grilled Onions, and Outlaw Sauce.OKaty Corral--Grilled chicken, Bacon, Shredded Cheese, Lettuce, and Truck-Made Avocado Cilantro Lime Ranch Dressing.Doc's Holliday--Think "Philly Cheesesteak wrapped up in a buttered/grilled PITA"! Shaved Steak, Hot N Gooey Monterey Jack Cheese Sauce, Grilled Bell Peppers & Onions.**Any grilled flatbread sandwich can be made into a burrito--JUST ASK!For private events with kids, we also offer Chicken Fingers and Mini Corn Dogs.LIMITED TIME SPECIALTY DESSERT, an Outlaw Original: DEEP FRIED CARAMEL APPLE O's--Award Winning, and available for a limited time! "EAT IT LIKE YOU STOLE IT!"
name: The Outlaw Grill
